short_description:
If you use torrent to download your favorite shows, maybe you have problems such as:
-remember the latest Torrent/episode downloaded;
-waste of time looking for new torrents to download;
-waste of time organizing the mess in the torrents' folder;
-waste of time looking for subtitles;

MyTvShowsOrganizer, hopefully, will solve all those problems for you.
MyTvShowsOrganizer is a simple program for WINDOWS (32/64 bit auto) to organize & download your favorite shows. It gets shows' name, episode (plus resolution and release) and search the web at the chosen torrent indexer site. Then, the magnet link for the more seeded realease is sent to your torrent client (like utorrent). It has several more cool tools to make your experience with torrents, a very nice one.

You are going to need WINDOWS 64 bit (native), 32 bit (compatible) and an installed torrent client like utorrent.

